name: You ready?
description: Are you ready to taste the lemon? Are you ready to understand what freedom tastes like? ‘You ready?’ is the sixth and last nft in the second part of the lemon collection. The second part of the lemon collection tells the rest of the story in 6 illustrations. This part is about becoming and sharing the lemon. Digital artwork made in 2021 by Camila Trapasso (camamblo).
